reviews.review_text:
1st show! Thank you so much for posting the entire show!
What a trip this was for me. 19 years old and seeing the band I loved for the first time live.
WOW!! I had no idea what I was in for. The Dead (and 2 fat pink lips) took me on a ride I will never forget. I was a puppet on a string for the duration of the show. We made our way up front right in front of Bobby, and when Jerry broke out the first G-C-G strumming chords of Bertha I knew I was where I was supposed to be. I was home.
